<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Farmer Tips | FarmNet</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f4f4f4;
}

/* NAVBAR */

.navbar{
    width:100%;
    background:#008000;
    padding:18px 50px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
    z-index:1000;
}

.logo{
    color:white;
    font-size:32px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.nav-links a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    margin-left:30px;
    font-size:17px;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.nav-links a:hover{
    color:#dcedc8;
}

/* HERO SECTION */

.hero{
    height:300px;
    background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),
    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500937386664-56d1dfef3854?q=80&w=1200');
    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:55px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero p{
    font-size:22px;
}

/* MAIN CONTAINER */

.container{
    width:90%;
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:50px auto;
}

/* SECTION TITLE */

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.section-title h2{
    font-size:40px;
    color:#1b5e20;
}

.section-title p{
    color:#555;
    margin-top:10px;
    font-size:18px;
}

/* TIPS GRID */

.tips-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));
    gap:30px;
}

/* TIP CARD */

.tip-card{
    background:white;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:18px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transition:0.3s;
    border-top:6px solid #43a047;
}

.tip-card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.tip-icon{
    font-size:45px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.tip-card h3{
    color:#1b5e20;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    font-size:25px;
}

.tip-card p{
    color:#444;
    line-height:1.8;
    font-size:17px;
}

/* FOOTER */

.footer{
    background:#1b1b1b;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
    margin-top:50px;
}

.footer p{
    margin:5px 0;
}

/* MOBILE */

@media(max-width:768px){

    .navbar{
        flex-direction:column;
        gap:15px;
    }

    .nav-links{
        text-align:center;
    }

    .nav-links a{
        display:inline-block;
        margin:8px;
    }

    .hero h1{
        font-size:38px;
    }

    .hero p{
        font-size:18px;
    }

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->

<div class="navbar">

    <div class="logo">
        FARMNET
    </div>

    <div class="nav-links">

        <a href="/">Home</a>

        <a href="/predict">Crop Prediction</a>

        <a href="/blog">Discussion</a>

        <a href="/profile">Profile</a>

        <a href="/logout">Logout</a>

    </div>

</div>

<!-- HERO -->

<div class="hero">

    <div>

        <h1> Smart Farming Tips</h1>

        <p>Modern solutions for better crop productivity</p>

    </div>

</div>

<!-- MAIN -->

<div class="container">

    <div class="section-title">

        <h2>Practical Tips For Farmers</h2>

        <p>Useful agriculture practices to improve farming efficiency and crop yield.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="tips-grid">

        <!-- TIP 1 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">💧</div>

            <h3>Smart Irrigation</h3>

            <p>
                Water crops during early morning or evening to reduce evaporation.
                Drip irrigation saves water and improves plant growth efficiently.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 2 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">🌱</div>

            <h3>Soil Fertility</h3>

            <p>
                Use compost, organic manure, and bio-fertilizers regularly.
                Soil testing helps maintain proper Nitrogen, Phosphorus, and Potassium balance.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 3 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">🌾</div>

            <h3>Crop Rotation</h3>

            <p>
                Rotating crops every season improves soil nutrients and reduces diseases.
                It also prevents pest buildup in fields.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 4 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">🐛</div>

            <h3>Pest Management</h3>

            <p>
                Inspect leaves weekly for insects or fungus.
                Neem oil and eco-friendly pesticides reduce harmful chemical impact.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 5 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">☀️</div>

            <h3>Weather Monitoring</h3>

            <p>
                Check weather forecasts before irrigation or spraying pesticides.
                Avoid fertilizer spraying during rainfall periods.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 6 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">🚜</div>

            <h3>Modern Technology</h3>

            <p>
                Use weather apps, crop prediction systems, and smart farming tools
                to improve productivity and reduce farming risks.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 7 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">🌿</div>

            <h3>Weed Control</h3>

            <p>
                Remove weeds regularly because they consume nutrients from crops.
                Mulching helps retain soil moisture and suppress weed growth.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 8 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">🌦</div>

            <h3>Rainwater Harvesting</h3>

            <p>
                Store rainwater during monsoon season for irrigation in dry periods.
                This helps reduce water shortages during summer.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 9 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">🌻</div>

            <h3>Increase Crop Yield</h3>

            <p>
                Use certified quality seeds and maintain proper spacing between crops
                for healthy sunlight exposure and growth.
            </p>

        </div>

        <!-- TIP 10 -->

        <div class="tip-card">

            <div class="tip-icon">📦</div>

            <h3>Storage Management</h3>

            <p>
                Store grains in cool and dry places to prevent fungus and insect attacks.
                Proper storage reduces post-harvest losses.
            </p>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->

<div class="footer">

    <p>© 2026 FarmNet | Smart Agriculture Platform</p>

    <p>Helping Farmers with Technology 🌱</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>